snippet.title: Do No Harm - Gameplay Trailer | Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
A Doctor Simulator with a Lovecraftian twist.
WISHLIST on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3138780/Do_No_Harm/

Diagnose patients by analyzing unsettling symptoms and treat them using your Book of Medicine. Make moral choices — decide who to save or kill, discover whom to trust, and unlock multiple endings! Can you endure 30 days of perilous decisions?

#DoNoHarmGame  #indiegame #doctorgame #lovecraft #cthulhumythos
